title: Annual Family Turkey Feed
desc: Every year we all come together for the Turkey Feed where we give thanks together as a church family. Bring your friends and family out along with your best side dish or dessert. We are asking all of our Word of Life family to help make this dinner celebration possible by signing up to bring something. ??We will fill up quick so reserve your seat! ?RSVP with the amount of people attending. ? We will be celebrating together as a church family therefore all children will be seated with their parents for dinner. ? ? Pastor Elvira Lozano (714) 606-2621 ??
